    "body": "Or possibly 'system if I'm root, user otherwise', since installing to root's home directory will not usually be helpful - it would be smarter to fail in that case.\n\nI have some admin stuff to do this morning, but I could work on it, or review a PR, later. The relevant pieces of the code start here:\n\nhttps://github.com/ipython/ipython/blob/master/IPython/kernel/kernelspec.py#L140\n"
